          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Disclosure of Tax Havens and Offshoring Act </b></p> <p>This bill requires certain issuers of securities to annually disclose information related to the tax jurisdiction, income, and assets of their constituent entities on a country-by-country basis. </p>]]>
